PREAMBLE

The Light General License (LGL) is designed to allow free use of the Software 
for internal business operations while protecting the project's sustainability. 
It permits free use, modification, and internal business use, while requiring 
a Commercial License for distribution, integration into commercial products, 
or use as a service. This ensures the project remains actively developed and 
maintained.

