"Internal Business Use" means using the Software solely within your organization 
for your own business operations, NOT including any of the activities in 
"Commercial Distribution" below.

"Commercial Distribution" means:
(a) Selling, reselling, or sublicensing the Software to third parties
(b) Offering the Software as a hosted or managed service (SaaS) to external customers
